---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Call Forwarding - Immediate, Busy, No Answer - GonoPBX" description="GonoPBX call forwarding: immediate, busy, and no-answer forwarding per extension. Enable via toggle in the web GUI." lang="en">

  
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/en/rufumleitungen" class="nav-logo">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="GonoPBX Logo" />
      </a>
      <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="Menu">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M3 12h18M3 6h18M3 18h18" />
        </svg>
      </button>
      <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
        <li><a href="/en/#features">Features</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/#screenshots">Screenshots</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/#techstack">Technology</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/release-notes">Release Notes</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/blog/">Blog</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/kontakt">Contact</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/unterstuetzen">Support</a></li>
        <li class="nav-lang">
          <a href="/rufumleitungen" class="lang-link">DE</a>
          <span class="lang-sep">|</span>
          <a href="/en/rufumleitungen" class="lang-link active">EN</a>
        </li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/ankaios76/gonopbx" class="nav-cta">GitHub</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>


  <section class="blog-article">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/en/#features" class="blog-back-link">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
        Back to overview
      </a>

      <div class="blog-article-header">
        <div class="blog-card-meta" style="justify-content:center;">
          <span class="blog-card-tag">Feature</span>
          <span>Core capability</span>
        </div>
        <h1>Call Forwarding – Route Calls Intelligently</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="blog-article-content">
        <p>
          Call forwarding ensures that <strong>no call is lost</strong>.
          Per extension you can configure three forwarding types –
          each with a destination and a toggle to activate it.
        </p>

        <h2>Forwarding types</h2>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Immediate (Unconditional)</strong> – All calls are forwarded instantly without ringing</li>
          <li><strong>Busy</strong> – Forward only when the extension is busy</li>
          <li><strong>No Answer</strong> – Forward after a configurable timeout (e.g., 20 seconds)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Screenshot</h2>

        <div style="margin:32px 0;">
          <img src="/feature-rufumleitungen.png" alt="Call forwarding in GonoPBX" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);" />
          <p style="text-align:center;color:#718096;font-size:0.9rem;margin-top:8px;">Per-extension forwarding with toggle activation</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Features in detail</h2>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Toggle per type</strong> – Enable or disable each forwarding type independently</li>
          <li><strong>Internal &amp; external destinations</strong> – Forward to other extensions or external numbers</li>
          <li><strong>Instant activation</strong> – Changes apply immediately in the dialplan</li>
          <li><strong>Combinable</strong> – Busy and No Answer forwarding can be active at the same time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Typical scenarios</h2>

        <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:24px 0;">
          <thead>
            <tr style="border-bottom:2px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:left;">
              <th style="padding:12px 16px;color:#4a5568;">Scenario</th>
              <th style="padding:12px 16px;color:#4a5568;">Setting</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Vacation / absence</td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Immediate forwarding to backup or mobile</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Busy fallback</td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Busy forwarding to voicemail or colleague</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Missed call</td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">No Answer forwarding after 20s to voicemail</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class="blog-info-box">
          <p>
            <strong>Available since the first release.</strong>
            Call forwarding is implemented in the dialplan and takes effect immediately.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <ul class="footer-links">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/ankaios76/gonopbx">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://demo.gonopbx.de">Live Demo</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/unterstuetzen">Support</a></li>
        <li><a href="/impressum">Imprint</a></li>
        <li><a href="/datenschutz">Privacy</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>&copy; 2026 Norbert Hengsteler. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>


  <script>
    document.getElementById('navToggle')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.getElementById('navLinks')?.classList.toggle('open');
    });
    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-links a').forEach(link => {
      link.addEventListener('click', () => {
        document.getElementById('navLinks')?.classList.remove('open');
      });
    });
  </script>

</Layout>
